most popular locations based cc_data

cc_data %>%
  mutate(location = fct_infreq(location)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = location)) + 
  geom_bar()+
  ylim(0,250) +
  geom_text(stat="count", 
      aes(label=paste0(..count.., ", ", 
      round(..count../sum(..count..)*100,
            1), "%")),
      vjust=-1) +
  xlab("location") +
  ylab("Count") +
  theme(axis.title.y=element_text(angle = 0))+
  coord_flip()
